    "title": "Attic & Loft Clearance in Canons Town | Based in Canons Town",
    "body_content": "<!doctype html>\n\n\n\n<header class=\"site-header\">\n  <div class=\"header-inner\">\n    <a href=\"/\" class=\"header-logo\">Cornwall Waste Clearance</a>\n    \n    <div class=\"header-cta\">\n      <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"header-phone\">\ud83d\udcde 07347 300788</a>\n      <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"header-btn\">Free Quote</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n<div class=\"hero-img\"></div>\n<h1 class=\"page-h1\">Attic & Loft Clearance in Canons Town | Based in Canons Town</h1>\n\n<section class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"container content-narrow\">\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <div class=\"trust-banner\">\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2764\ufe0f Local Family Business</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2b50 123 Five-Star Reviews</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2705 134 Clearances This Year</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udfc6 14+ Years Experience</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u267b\ufe0f Environment Agency Registered</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udf3f Eco-Friendly & Recycling</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udf81 Charity Donations Where Possible</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83d\udcde Free Quotes \u2014 No Obligation</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83d\udd50 Mon\u2013Sat 7am\u20137pm</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"location-intro\">Canons-Town's scattered farmhouses and converted barns sit along country lanes with limited passing places and no street lighting. Many properties have muddy tracks, soft ground, and outbuildings that are difficult to reach. Cornwall Waste Clearance sends in a high-clearance Vauxhall Movano, with crews transferring waste to the vehicle using heavy-duty sacks carried from outbuildings.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"padding:0 0 8px 0\"><div class=\"before-after-gallery\">\n  <div class=\"before-after-item\">\n    <img src=\"/assets/images/drive-before.webp\" alt=\"Before driveway clearance by Cornwall Waste Clearance\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n    <span class=\"before-after-label\">Before</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"before-after-item\">\n    <img src=\"/assets/images/drive-after.webp\" alt=\"After driveway clearance by Cornwall Waste Clearance\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n    <span class=\"before-after-label\">After</span>\n  </div>\n</div></div>\n\n<h2>Safe, Insured Loft Clearance \u2014 No Ladder Needed.</h2>\n      <p>Loft spaces in Canons Town accumulate decades of stored items \u2014 old furniture, boxes, clothing, toys and forgotten belongings. Cornwall Waste Clearance provides professional attic and loft clearance services, safely removing everything and leaving the space completely empty.</p>\n      <p>Working in loft spaces requires care. Our team is experienced in protecting your ceilings, hatch surrounds and landing areas while clearing even the most packed attics safely and efficiently.</p>\n      <div class=\"cta-buttons\">\n        <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"btn btn-green\">&#128222; Call: 07347 300788</a>\n        <a href=\"#quote\" class=\"btn btn-dark\">&#9993;&#65039; Get a Free Quote</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Access &amp; Safety \u2014 How We Work</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>We assess the access point (hatch, ladder, pull-down stairs) before starting</li>\n        <li>Floor protection is laid on landings and stairs to prevent damage</li>\n        <li>Items are carefully passed down rather than dropped or thrown</li>\n        <li>We check for fragile ceilings and boardless sections before walking the loft</li>\n        <li>All electricals and insulation are treated with care</li>\n        <li>We will flag any concerns (damp, structural issues, pest evidence) we notice during the clearance</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>What We Commonly Find in Canons Town Lofts</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Old suitcases, bags and travel accessories</li>\n        <li>Boxes of books, paperwork and magazines</li>\n        <li>Children's toys, games and clothing from years past</li>\n        <li>Old furniture too large to bring downstairs easily</li>\n        <li>Christmas decorations, seasonal items and displays</li>\n        <li>Old electrical equipment \u2014 TVs, stereos, computers</li>\n        <li>Sports equipment and hobby materials</li>\n        <li>General long-term storage that has simply built up over years</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Preparing for Your Loft Clearance</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Set aside anything you want to keep \u2014 we will work around it</li>\n        <li>Make sure the hatch is accessible (remove any furniture beneath it)</li>\n        <li>Let us know if there is no fixed ladder \u2014 we bring our own if needed</li>\n        <li>You do not need to sort, bag or move anything else</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Pricing Guide for Canons Town</h2>\n      <p>Loft clearance prices depend on volume and access difficulty:</p>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Small loft (a few items): <strong>from \u00a3100</strong></li>\n        <li>Standard loft clearance: <strong>\u00a3200\u2013\u00a3400</strong></li>\n        <li>Large or heavily packed loft: <strong>\u00a3400\u2013\u00a3600</strong></li>\n        <li>Loft plus garage or shed: <strong>from \u00a3500</strong></li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>What if my loft has no fixed ladder or boarding in Canons Town?</strong>\n        <p>No problem \u2014 we bring our own ladder and are experienced in working in unboarded lofts. We will take extra care to stay on joists and protect your ceiling.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Are there asbestos boards in older lofts?</strong>\n        <p>Some older properties have asbestos insulation boards. If you suspect asbestos is present, we can advise \u2014 asbestos requires a specialist licensed contractor before we can proceed with the clearance.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Will you damage my ceiling or hatch during the clearance?</strong>\n        <p>We take every precaution to protect your property. Floor protection is laid, and all items are carefully passed through the hatch. We have never left a property damaged.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Can you clear a loft that has not been accessed for 20+ years?</strong>\n        <p>Yes \u2014 this is very common. We will assess the access and contents before starting and keep you informed throughout. No matter how long items have been up there, we will clear them.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Are you a licensed waste carrier?</strong>\n        <p>Yes. Cornwall Waste Clearance is fully registered with the Environment Agency. All items are recycled, donated or legally disposed of \u2014 nothing is fly-tipped.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>More Clearance Services in Canons Town</h2>\n      <div class=\"location-grid\">\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-canons-town/\" class=\"loc-link\">\ud83c\udfe1 House Clearance</a>\n        <a href=\"/rubbish-clearance-canons-town/\" class=\"loc-link\">\ud83d\ude9b Rubbish Clearance</a>\n        <a href=\"/garage-shed-clearance-canons-town/\" class=\"loc-link\">\ud83d\ude97 Garage & Shed Clearance</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-canons-town/\" class=\"loc-link\">\u26b1\ufe0f Bereavement & Probate Clearance</a>\n        <a href=\"/hoarder-clearance-canons-town/\" class=\"loc-link\">\ud83c\udfe0 Hoarder Clearance</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <div class=\"map-wrapper\">\n        <iframe src=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Canons+Town+Cornwall&output=embed\"\n          width=\"100%\" height=\"300\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"quote\" class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Request a Free Quote in Canons Town</h2>\n      <form method=\"POST\" action=\"/send.php\">\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"first-name\">First Name *</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"first-name\" name=\"first-name\" required>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"surname\">Surname *</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"surname\" name=\"surname\" required>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"telephone\">Telephone *</label>\n          <input type=\"tel\" id=\"telephone\" name=\"telephone\" required>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"postcode\">Postcode *</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"postcode\" name=\"postcode\" required>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"clearance-type\">Clearance Type *</label>\n          <select id=\"clearance-type\" name=\"clearance-type\" required>\n            <option value=\"\">Please select...</option>\n            <option value=\"House/Flat/Bungalow\">House / Flat / Bungalow</option>\n            <option value=\"Garage/Garden/Shed\">Garage / Garden / Shed</option>\n            <option value=\"Attic/Loft\">Attic / Loft</option>\n            <option value=\"Bereavement/Probate\">Bereavement / Probate</option>\n            <option value=\"Hoarder\">Hoarder Property</option>\n            <option value=\"Commercial/Industrial\">Commercial / Industrial</option>\n          </select>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"message\">Message</label>\n          <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\"></textarea>\n        </div>\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-primary\">Send Enquiry</button>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n<div class=\"nearby-locations\">\n  <h3>Also Serving Nearby Areas</h3>\n  <div class=\"nearby-pills\">\n<span class=\"nearby-pill\">Bodmin</span>\n<span class=\"nearby-pill\">Lostwithiel</span>\n<span class=\"nearby-pill\">St Austell</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n\n<a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"quote-now-btn\" aria-label=\"Get a free quote from Cornwall Waste Clearance\">Free Quote</a>\n<a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"call-now-btn\" aria-label=\"Call Cornwall Waste Clearance now\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"white\"><path d=\"M6.6 10.8c1.4 2.8 3.8 5.1 6.6 6.6l2.2-2.2c.3-.3.7-.4 1-.2 1.1.4 2.3.6 3.6.6.6 0 1 .4 1 1V20c0 .6-.4 1-1 1C10.6 21 3 13.4 3 4c0-.6.4-1 1-1h3.5c.6 0 1 .4 1 1 0 1.3.2 2.5.6 3.6.1.3 0 .7-.2 1L6.6 10.8z\"/></svg></a>\n<script src=\"/assets/js/main.js\"></script>"
