    "title": "Bereavement Clearance Cornwall | Based in Cornwall",
    "body_content": "<!doctype html>\n\n\n\n<header class=\"site-header\">\n  <div class=\"header-inner\">\n    <a href=\"/\" class=\"header-logo\">Cornwall Waste Clearance</a>\n    \n    <div class=\"header-cta\">\n      <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"header-phone\">\ud83d\udcde 07347 300788</a>\n      <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"header-btn\">Free Quote</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n<div class=\"hero-img\"></div>\n<h1 class=\"page-h1\">Bereavement Clearance Cornwall | Based in Cornwall</h1>\n\n<div class=\"trust-banner\">\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2764\ufe0f Local Family Business</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2b50 123 Five-Star Reviews</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2705 134 Clearances This Year</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udfc6 14+ Years Experience</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u267b\ufe0f Environment Agency Registered</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udf3f Eco-Friendly & Recycling</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udf81 Charity Donations Where Possible</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83d\udcde Free Quotes \u2014 No Obligation</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83d\udd50 Mon\u2013Sat 7am\u20137pm</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"padding:0 0 8px 0\"><div class=\"before-after-gallery\">\n        <div class=\"before-after-item\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/Before Rubbish Removal.webp\" alt=\"Before rubbish removal by Cornwall Waste Clearance\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n          <span class=\"before-after-label\">Before</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"before-after-item\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/After Rubbish Removal.webp\" alt=\"After rubbish removal by Cornwall Waste Clearance\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n          <span class=\"before-after-label\">After</span>\n        </div>\n      </div></div>\n<h2>Handled With Care, Discretion & No Rush.</h2>\n<section class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"container content-narrow\">\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <p>Losing a loved one is difficult enough without the added burden of clearing their property. Cornwall Waste Clearance provides a sensitive, discreet bereavement clearance service across Cornwall. Our team works with empathy and respect at every step, giving families the time and space they need.</p>\n      <div class=\"cta-buttons\">\n        <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"btn btn-green\">&#128222; Call: 07347 300788</a>\n        <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"btn btn-dark\">&#9993;&#65039; Get a Free Quote</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>What We Clear</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Full property clearance</li>\n        <li>Furniture and personal belongings</li>\n        <li>Clothing and textiles</li>\n        <li>Valuables identified and set aside</li>\n        <li>Donations to local charities arranged</li>\n        <li>Responsible disposal of remaining items</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Areas We Cover in Cornwall</h2>\n      <p>We provide bereavement clearance cornwall services across all of Cornwall. Select your area below:</p>\n      <div class=\"location-grid\">\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-ashton/\" class=\"loc-link\">Ashton</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-blackwater/\" class=\"loc-link\">Blackwater</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-bodinnick/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bodinnick</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-bodmin/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bodmin</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-boscastle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Boscastle</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-breage/\" class=\"loc-link\">Breage</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-bude/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bude</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-budock-water/\" class=\"loc-link\">Budock Water</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-bugle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bugle</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-callington/\" class=\"loc-link\">Callington</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-calstock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Calstock</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-camborne/\" class=\"loc-link\">Camborne</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-camelford/\" class=\"loc-link\">Camelford</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-canons-town/\" class=\"loc-link\">Canons Town</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-carbis-bay/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carbis Bay</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-carey-park/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carey Park</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-carharrack/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carharrack</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-carlyon-bay/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carlyon Bay</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-carnon-downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carnon Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-cawsand/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cawsand</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-chacewater/\" class=\"loc-link\">Chacewater</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-connor-downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Connor Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-constantine/\" class=\"loc-link\">Constantine</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-cornwall/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cornwall</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-crantock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Crantock</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-crowlas/\" class=\"loc-link\">Crowlas</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-cubert/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cubert</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-delabole/\" class=\"loc-link\">Delabole</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-devoran/\" class=\"loc-link\">Devoran</a>\n        <a href=\"/berea