class=\"content-block\">\n      <p>Cornwall Waste Clearance is a local family business providing professional house clearance services across Cornwall. Whether you need a full property cleared after a move, sale, bereavement or tenancy change, our experienced team handles everything with care and efficiency. We are fully licensed with the Environment Agency and recycle or donate as much as possible.</p>\n      <div class=\"cta-buttons\">\n        <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"btn btn-green\">&#128222; Call: 07347 300788</a>\n        <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"btn btn-dark\">&#9993;&#65039; Get a Free Quote</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>What We Clear</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Furniture and white goods</li>\n        <li>Clothing and personal effects</li>\n        <li>Boxes and general clutter</li>\n        <li>Garden items and tools</li>\n        <li>Carpets and flooring</li>\n        <li>Electrical appliances</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Areas We Cover in Cornwall</h2>\n      <p>We provide house clearance cornwall services across all of Cornwall. Select your area below:</p>\n      <div class=\"location-grid\">\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-ashton/\" class=\"loc-link\">Ashton</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-blackwater/\" class=\"loc-link\">Blackwater</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-bodinnick/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bodinnick</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-bodmin/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bodmin</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-boscastle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Boscastle</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-breage/\" class=\"loc-link\">Breage</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-bude/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bude</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-budock-water/\" class=\"loc-link\">Budock Water</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-bugle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bugle</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-callington/\" class=\"loc-link\">Callington</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-calstock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Calstock</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-camborne/\" class=\"loc-link\">Camborne</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-camelford/\" class=\"loc-link\">Camelford</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-canons-town/\" class=\"loc-link\">Canons Town</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-carbis-bay/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carbis Bay</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-carey-park/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carey Park</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-carharrack/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carharrack</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-carlyon-bay/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carlyon Bay</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-carnon-downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carnon Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-cawsand/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cawsand</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-chacewater/\" class=\"loc-link\">Chacewater</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-connor-downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Connor Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-constantine/\" class=\"loc-link\">Constantine</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-cornwall/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cornwall</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-crantock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Crantock</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-crowlas/\" class=\"loc-link\">Crowlas</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-cubert/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cubert</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-delabole/\" class=\"loc-link\">Delabole</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-devoran/\" class=\"loc-link\">Devoran</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-dobwalls/\" class=\"loc-link\">Dobwalls</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-downderry/\" class=\"loc-link\">Downderry</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-duporth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Duporth</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-egloshayle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Egloshayle</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-falmouth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Falmouth</a>\