/\" class=\"loc-link\">Pensilva</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-penwith/\" class=\"loc-link\">Penwith</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-penwithick/\" class=\"loc-link\">Penwithick</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-penzance/\" class=\"loc-link\">Penzance</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-perranarworthal/\" class=\"loc-link\">Perranarworthal</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-perranporth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Perranporth</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-playing-place/\" class=\"loc-link\">Playing Place</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-polgooth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Polgooth</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-polperro/\" class=\"loc-link\">Polperro</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-polruan/\" class=\"loc-link\">Polruan</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-ponsanooth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Ponsanooth</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-pool/\" class=\"loc-link\">Pool</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-port-isaac/\" class=\"loc-link\">Port Isaac</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-porthleven/\" class=\"loc-link\">Porthleven</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-porthtowan/\" class=\"loc-link\">Porthtowan</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-portreath/\" class=\"loc-link\">Portreath</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-portscatho/\" class=\"loc-link\">Portscatho</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-praze-an-beeble/\" class=\"loc-link\">Praze an Beeble</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-probus/\" class=\"loc-link\">Probus</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-quintrell-downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Quintrell Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-reawla/\" class=\"loc-link\">Reawla</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-redruth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Redruth</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-roche/\" class=\"loc-link\">Roche</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-rock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Rock</a>\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-saltash/\" class=\"loc-link\">Saltash</a