    "slug": "office-clearance",
    "title": "Office Clearance Cornwall | Based in Cornwall",
    "body_content": "<!doctype html>\n\n\n\n<header class=\"site-header\">\n  <div class=\"header-inner\">\n    <a href=\"/\" class=\"header-logo\">Cornwall Waste Clearance</a>\n    \n    <div class=\"header-cta\">\n      <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"header-phone\">\ud83d\udcde 07347 300788</a>\n      <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"header-btn\">Free Quote</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n<div class=\"hero-img\"></div>\n<h1 class=\"page-h1\">Office Clearance Cornwall | Based in Cornwall</h1>\n\n<div class=\"trust-banner\">\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2764\ufe0f Local Family Business</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2b50 123 Five-Star Reviews</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2705 134 Clearances This Year</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udfc6 14+ Years Experience</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u267b\ufe0f Environment Agency Registered</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udf3f Eco-Friendly & Recycling</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udf81 Charity Donations Where Possible</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83d\udcde Free Quotes \u2014 No Obligation</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83d\udd50 Mon\u2013Sat 7am\u20137pm</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"padding:0 0 8px 0\"><div class=\"before-after-gallery\">\n        <div class=\"before-after-item\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/Before Rubbish Removal.webp\" alt=\"Before rubbish removal by Cornwall Waste Clearance\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n          <span class=\"before-after-label\">Before</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"before-after-item\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/After Rubbish Removal.webp\" alt=\"After rubbish removal by Cornwall Waste Clearance\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n          <span class=\"before-after-label\">After</span>\n        </div>\n      </div></div>\n<h2>Fast, Discreet Office Clearance \u2014 Free Quote.</h2>\n<section class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"container content-narrow\">\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <p>Cornwall Waste Clearance provides efficient, professional office clearance services across Cornwall. Whether you are relocating, refitting or closing, our team will clear your office quickly and responsibly, recycling and donating where possible.</p>\n      <div class=\"cta-buttons\">\n        <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"btn btn-green\">&#128222; Call: 07347 300788</a>\n        <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"btn btn-dark\">&#9993;&#65039; Get a Free Quote</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>What We Clear</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Desks, chairs and office furniture</li>\n        <li>IT equipment and electronics (WEEE compliant)</li>\n        <li>Filing cabinets and paperwork</li>\n        <li>Kitchen and breakout equipment</li>\n        <li>Carpets and partitioning</li>\n        <li>General office waste</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Areas We Cover in Cornwall</h2>\n      <p>We provide office clearance cornwall services across all of Cornwall. Select your area below:</p>\n      <div class=\"location-grid\">\n        <a href=\"/locations/Ashton/\" class=\"loc-link\">Ashton</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Blackwater/\" class=\"loc-link\">Blackwater</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Bodinnick/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bodinnick</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Bodmin/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bodmin</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Boscastle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Boscastle</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Breage/\" class=\"loc-link\">Breage</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Bude/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bude</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Budock-Water/\" class=\"loc-link\">Budock Water</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Bugle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bugle</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Callington/\" class=\"loc-link\">Callington</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Calstock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Calstock</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Camborne/\" class=\"loc-link\">Camborne</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Camelford/\" class=\"loc-link\">Camelford</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Canons-Town/\" class=\"loc-link\">Canons Town</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carbis-Bay/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carbis Bay</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carey-Park/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carey Park</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carharrack/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carharrack</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carlyon-Bay/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carlyon Bay</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carnon-Downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carnon Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Cawsand/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cawsand</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Chacewater/\" class=\"loc-link\">Chacewater</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Connor-Downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Connor Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Constantine/\" class=\"loc-link\">Constantine</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Cornwall/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cornwall</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Crantock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Crantock</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Crowlas/\" class=\"loc-link\">Crowlas</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Cubert/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cubert</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Delabole/\" class=\"loc-link\">Delabole</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Devoran/\" class=\"loc-link\">Devoran</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Dobwalls/\" class=\"loc-link\">Dobwalls</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Downderry/\" class=\"loc-link\">Downderry</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Duporth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Duporth</a>\n        \n        \n        <a href=\"/locations/Egloshayle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Egloshayle</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Falmouth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Falmouth</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Flushing/\" class=\"loc-link\">Flushing</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Four-Lanes/\" class=\"loc-link\">Four Lanes</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Fowey/\" class=\"loc-link\">Fowey</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Foxhole/\" clas