u2014 you fill a skip yourself. We do all the lifting and carrying for you.</li>\n        <li><strong>No wait</strong> \u2014 skip hire can take days to arrange and collect. We are often available same week.</li>\n        <li><strong>No restrictions</strong> \u2014 skips have prohibited items. We handle most things skips will not take.</li>\n        <li><strong>No eyesore</strong> \u2014 a skip sits outside your property for days. We arrive, load and go.</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>What We Accept</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Household furniture and white goods</li>\n        <li>Garden waste \u2014 green waste, soil, rubble in small quantities</li>\n        <li>General household junk and clutter</li>\n        <li>Electrical items and appliances</li>\n        <li>Scrap metal</li>\n        <li>Mattresses and soft furnishings</li>\n        <li>DIY waste \u2014 timber, plasterboard, tiles</li>\n        <li>Commercial rubbish \u2014 offices, shops, small businesses</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>What We Cannot Take</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Asbestos (requires specialist licensed contractor)</li>\n        <li>Clinical or medical waste</li>\n        <li>Chemicals, solvents or pesticides in large quantities</li>\n        <li>Firearms or ammunition</li>\n      </ul>\n      <p>If you are unsure whether we can take something, just call us on 07347 300788 and we will advise.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Pricing Guide for Praze An Beeble</h2>\n      <p>Prices are based on the volume of waste loaded onto our vehicle:</p>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Minimum load (a few items): <strong>from \u00a360</strong></li>\n        <li>Quarter load: <strong>\u00a3100\u2013\u00a3150</strong></li>\n        <li>Half load: <strong>\u00a3150\u2013\u00a3250</strong></li>\n        <li>Full load: <strong>\u00a3300\u2013\u00a3500</strong></li>\n        <li>Multiple loads / large clearances: <strong>POA</strong></li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Can you collect rubbish the same day in Praze An Beeble?</strong>\n        <p>We aim to offer same-week collection across Cornwall. Same-day availability depends on our schedule \u2014 call 07347 300788 and we will do our best.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Do I need to bag the rubbish before you arrive?</strong>\n        <p>No \u2014 you do not need to bag, sort or move anything. Our team carries everything from wherever it is in the property.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Can you collect mixed loads \u2014 different types of waste together?</strong>\n        <p>Yes \u2014 mixed loads are no problem. We sort everything ourselves at our facility to ensure responsible disposal and maximum recycling.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Do you collect commercial rubbish from businesses in Praze An Beeble?</strong>\n        <p>Yes \u2014 we collect rubbish from offices, shops, warehouses and other commercial premises. Call us for a tailored quote.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"faq-item\">\n        <strong>Are you a licensed waste carrier?</strong>\n        <p>Yes. Cornwall Waste Clearance is fully registered with the Environment Agency. You will never be held liable for illegally disposed waste when you use our service.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>More Clearance Services in Praze An Beeble</h2>\n      <div class=\"location-grid\">\n        <a href=\"/house-clearance-praze-an-beeble/\" class=\"loc-link\">\ud83c\udfe1 House Clearance</a>\n        <a href=\"/garage-shed-clearance-praze-an-beeble/\" class=\"loc-link\">\ud83d\ude97 Garage & Shed Clearance</a>\n        <a href=\"/attic-clearance-praze-an-beeble/\" class=\"loc-link\">\ud83c\udfe0 Attic Clearance</a>\n        <a href=\"/bereavement-probate-clearance-praze-an-beeble/\" class=\"loc-link\">\u26b1\ufe0f Bereavement & Probate Clearance</a>\n        <a href=\"/hoarder-clearance-praze-an-beeble/\" class=\"loc-link\">\ud83c\udfe0 Hoarder Clearance</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <div class=\"map-wrapper\">\n        <iframe src=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Praze+An+Beeble+Cornwall&output=embed\"\n          width=\"100%\" height=\"300\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"quote\" class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Request a Free Quote in Praze An Beeble</h2>\n      <form method=\"POST\" action=\"/send.php\">\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"first-name\">First Name *</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"first-name\" name=\"first-name\" required>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"surname\">Surname *</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"surname\" name=\"surname\" required>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"telephone\">Telephone *</label>\n          <input type=\"tel\" id=\"telephone\" name=\"telephone\" required>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"postcode\">Postcode *</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"postcode\" name=\"postcode\" required>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"clearance-type\">Clearance Type *</label>\n          <select id=\"clearance-type\" name=\"clearance-type\" required>\n            <option value=\"\">Please select...</option>\n            <option value=\"House/Flat/Bungalow\">House / Flat / Bungalow</option>\n            <option value=\"Garage/Garden/Shed\">Garage / Garden / Shed</option>\n            <option value=\"Attic/Loft\">Attic / Loft</option>\n            <option value=\"Bereavement/Probate\">Bereavement / Probate</option>\n            <option value=\"Hoarder\">Hoarder Property</option>\n            <option value=\"Commercial/Industrial\">Commercial / Industrial</option>\n          </select>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"message\">Message</label>\n          <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\"></textarea>\n        </div>\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-primary\">Send Enquiry</button>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n<div class=\"nearby-locations\">\n  <h3>Also Serving Nearby Areas</h3>\n  <div class=\"nearby-pills\">\n<span class=\"nearby-pill\">Camborne</span>\n<span class=\"nearby-pill\">Helston</span>\n<span class=\"nearby-pill\">Crowlas</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</section>",
    "description": "Man and van rubbish removals in Praze An Beeble \u2014 fast and reliable. Save time and money on your waste disposal and recycling needs. Call 07347 300788 Monday to Saturday 7am to 7pm."
  },
  {
    "slug": "privacy-policy",
    "title": "Privacy Policy | Cornwall Waste Clearance",
    "body_content": "<section class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"container content-narrow\">\n\n    <h2>Who We Are</h2>\n    <p>Cornwall Waste Clearance operates the website cornwallwasteclearance.co.uk. This privacy policy explains how we collect and use personal data when you visit our website or contact us.</p>\n\n    <h2>What Data We Collect</h2>\n    <p>We may collect the following information when you submit our contact form or call us:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Name</li>\n      <li>Telephone number</li>\n      <li>Postcode</li>\n      <li>Details of the clearance service you require</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>We also collect standard website analytics data (pages visited, time on site, device type) via anonymised tools.</p>\n\n    <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>\n    <p>We use the information you provide solely to respond to your enquiry and to provide the clearance services you request. We do not sell, rent or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>\n\n    <h2>Data Retention</h2>\n    <p>We retain enquiry data for up to 12 months. After this period, it is securely deleted unless we are legally required to retain it longer.</p>\n\n    <h2>Your Rights</h2>\n    <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>\n      <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>\n      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>\n      <li>Object to processing of your data</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>To exercise any of these rights, please call us on <a href=\"tel:07347300788\">07347 300788</a>.</p>\n\n    <h2>Cookies</h2>\n    <p>We use essential cookies to ensure our website functions correctly. For more detail, please see our <a href=\"/cookie-policy/\">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>\n\n    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>\n    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on this page.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
    "description": "Privacy policy for Cornwall Waste Clearance \u2014 how we collect, use and protect your personal data."
  },
  {
    "slug": "probate-clearance-cornwall",
    "title": "Probate Clearance Cornwall | Cornwall Waste Clearance",
    "body_content": "<!doctype html>\n\n\n\n<header class=\"site-header\">\n  <div class=\"header-inner\">\n    <a href=\"/\" class=\"header-logo\">Cornwall Waste Clearance</a>\n    \n    <div class=\"header-cta\">\n      <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"header-phone\">\ud83d\udcde 07347 300788</a>\n      <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"header-btn\">Free Quote</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n<div class=\"hero-img\"></div>\n<h1 class=\"page-h1\">Probate Clearance Cornwall | Cornwall Waste Clearance</h1>\n\n<div class=\"trust-banner\">\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2b50 123 Five-Star Reviews</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2705 134 Clearances This Year</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udfc6 14+ Years Experience</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u267b\ufe0f Environment Agency Registered</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udf3f Eco-Friendly & Recycling</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\u2764\ufe0f Local Family Business</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83c\udf81 Charity Donations Where Possible</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83d\udcde Free Quotes \u2014 No Obligation</div>\n  <div class=\"trust-item\">\ud83d\udd50 Mon\u2013Sat 7am\u20137pm</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"padding:0 0 8px 0\"><div class=\"before-after-gallery\">\n        <div class=\"before-after-item\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/Before Rubbish Removal.webp\" alt=\"Before rubbish removal by Cornwall Waste Clearance\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n          <span class=\"before-after-label\">Before</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"before-after-item\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/images/After Rubbish Removal.webp\" alt=\"After rubbish removal by Cornwall Waste Clearance\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n          <span class=\"before-after-label\">After</span>\n        </div>\n      </div></div>\n<section class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"container content-narrow\">\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <p>Cornwall Waste Clearance works with solicitors, executors and families to provide professional probate clearance services across Cornwall. We understand the sensitivity required and work efficiently to help move the probate process forward.</p>\n      <div class=\"cta-buttons\">\n        <a href=\"tel:07347300788\" class=\"btn btn-green\">&#128222; Call: 07347 300788</a>\n        <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"btn btn-dark\">&#9993;&#65039; Get a Free Quote</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>What We Clear</h2>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Full property clearance for estate purposes</li>\n        <li>Furniture, appliances and personal effects</li>\n        <li>Documentation and paperwork handled carefully</li>\n        <li>Valuables identified and set aside for executors</li>\n        <li>Donations and recycling arranged</li>\n        <li>Clean and empty property handed back promptly</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"content-block\">\n      <h2>Areas We Cover in Cornwall</h2>\n      <p>We provide probate clearance cornwall services across all of Cornwall. Select your area below:</p>\n      <div class=\"location-grid\">\n        <a href=\"/locations/Ashton/\" class=\"loc-link\">Ashton</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Blackwater/\" class=\"loc-link\">Blackwater</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Bodinnick/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bodinnick</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Bodmin/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bodmin</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Boscastle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Boscastle</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Breage/\" class=\"loc-link\">Breage</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Bude/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bude</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Budock-Water/\" class=\"loc-link\">Budock Water</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Bugle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Bugle</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Callington/\" class=\"loc-link\">Callington</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Calstock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Calstock</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Camborne/\" class=\"loc-link\">Camborne</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Camelford/\" class=\"loc-link\">Camelford</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Canons-Town/\" class=\"loc-link\">Canons Town</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carbis-Bay/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carbis Bay</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carey-Park/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carey Park</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carharrack/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carharrack</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carlyon-Bay/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carlyon Bay</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Carnon-Downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Carnon Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Cawsand/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cawsand</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Chacewater/\" class=\"loc-link\">Chacewater</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Connor-Downs/\" class=\"loc-link\">Connor Downs</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Constantine/\" class=\"loc-link\">Constantine</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Cornwall/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cornwall</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Crantock/\" class=\"loc-link\">Crantock</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Crowlas/\" class=\"loc-link\">Crowlas</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Cubert/\" class=\"loc-link\">Cubert</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Delabole/\" class=\"loc-link\">Delabole</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Devoran/\" class=\"loc-link\">Devoran</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Dobwalls/\" class=\"loc-link\">Dobwalls</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Downderry/\" class=\"loc-link\">Downderry</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Duporth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Duporth</a>\n        \n        \n        <a href=\"/locations/Egloshayle/\" class=\"loc-link\">Egloshayle</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Falmouth/\" class=\"loc-link\">Falmouth</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Flushing/\" class=\"loc-link\">Flushing</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Four-Lanes/\" class=\"loc-link\">Four Lanes</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/Fowey/\" class=\"loc-link\">Fowey</a>\n        <a href=\"/locations/