robate\">Bereavement / Probate</option>\n            <option value=\"Hoarder\">Hoarder Property</option>\n            <option value=\"Commercial/Industrial\">Commercial / Industrial</option>\n          </select>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <label for=\"message\">Message</label>\n          <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\"></textarea>\n        </div>\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-primary\">Send Enquiry</button>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
    "description": "Man and van rubbish removals in St Anns Chapel \u2014 fast and reliable. Save time and money on your waste disposal and recycling needs. Call 07347 300788 Monday to Saturday 7am to 7pm."
